headline: Trailblazing Taste: The PLANTERS® Brand Mixes Premium Nuts with Sweet Twists
summary: Calling all flavor chasers and snack-nut fanatics: The PLANTERS® brand is turning up the crunch with the launch of two trail mix blends that are anything but ordinary. Say hello to PLANTERS® White Chocolate Macadamia Nut and PLANTERS® Chocolate Caramel Pecan Crunch — two mixes designed to elevate snacking one delicious handful at a time.
